               <expan><abbr>ἐτ</abbr><ex>ῶν</ex></expan> <num>ο</num></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="deir0001.translation" corresp="#deir0001.diplomatic #deir0001.transcription">
            <p>Be of good courage, Dometianos(?)! Fifty years old.
                </p>
